{"type":"message","id":"e60a4ad2","parentId":"643fbd20","timestamp":"2026-03-09T21:02:02.274Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Mon 2026-03-09 16:02 CDT] [Subagent Context] You are running as a subagent (depth 1/1). Results auto-announce to your requester; do not busy-poll for status.\n\n[Subagent Task]: Message for Bryer: Tony says he loves the team. Start now on marketing builder: propose 5 quick wins to improve mission control clarity and actionability."}],"timestamp":1773090122271}}
{"type":"message","id":"74d7bf6a","parentId":"e60a4ad2","timestamp":"2026-03-09T21:02:07.995Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Here is the message for Bryer along with 5 quick wins to improve mission control clarity and actionability:\n\n---\n\nMessage for Bryer from Tony:\n\"Tony says he loves the team.\"\n\n5 Quick Wins to Improve Mission Control Clarity and Actionability:\n\n1. Simplify Dashboard Layout: Reduce clutter by grouping related metrics and tasks visually, using clear headings and collapsible sections to help users focus on priority items.\n\n2. Add Contextual Tooltips: Provide brief explanations or actionable hints on key metrics and controls so users understand their meaning and potential next steps without leaving the page.\n\n3. Implement Real-time Alerts: Highlight urgent issues or status changes with color-coded banners or notifications that link directly to relevant dashboards or controls for immediate action.\n\n4. Use Action-oriented Labels: Rename buttons, tabs, and filters with clear verbs that describe the intended action, e.g., \"Resolve Issue,\" \"Assign Task,\" or \"Review Report.\"\n\n5. Provide Quick Filters and Presets: Enable users to apply common filters or views (e.g., high priority only, team-specific data) with one click to speed up decision-making and navigation.\n\n---\n\nLet me know if you want me to send this message to Bryer directly or make any adjustments.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_03bab87b8b52ba6a0069af354c78108191b44f13df8673d50a\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-4.1-mini","usage":{"input":8498,"output":249,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":8747,"cost":{"input":0.0033992000000000002,"output":0.00039840000000000003,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0037976000000000004}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773090122273}}
